           rdfs:domain :Organization ;
           rdfs:range :Person .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/47ila/ontologies/2026/1/untitled-ontology-7/hasTime
:hasTime rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
         rdfs:subPropertyOf owl:topObjectProperty ;
